  <purpose>&lt;a id=&quot;Top&quot; name=&quot;Top&quot;>&lt;/a> &#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The purpose of this task is to define a common vocabulary that can be used in all textual descriptions of the system,&#xD;
    especially the software requirements.&#xD;
&lt;/p></purpose>
